1972;;When the Legends Die;;American;;Stuart Millar;;Richard Widmark, Frederic Forrest;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/When_the_Legends_Die;;A Ute Indian youth, Tom Black Bull (Frederic Forrest), leaves the reservation to enter the rodeo life. He is under the tutelage of Red Dillon (Richard Widmark), a talented man with a drinking problem. The youth deals with the struggle between two worlds and deciding what life has to offer.